# Architecture Decision Records

This directory contains Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) for this project.
This file is an index of all ADRs, generated automatically on {{.Date}}.
See the [Index Section](#index) below for the last updated ADRs.

## What is an ADR?

An Architecture Decision Record captures an important architectural decision,
including the context in which it was made and its consequences.

